            "title": "Living Room Re-Creation in Half Life: Alyx",
            "summary": "Modeled using Autodesk Maya and Adobe Substance/Photoshop. Click Here to play mod Kotaku and 80.lv articles :D",
            "content_html": "<p class=\"align-center\">Modeled using Autodesk Maya and Adobe Substance/Photoshop. <a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2806633112\">Click Here</a> to play mod</p>\n<div class=\"post__video align-center\"><div class=\"post__iframe\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" width=\"693\" height=\"388\" style=\"width: 693px; height: 388px;\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/-mh5cQ6dC4Y\" title=\"Video\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></div><a href=\"https://kotaku.com/half-life-vr-virtual-reality-mod-custom-3d-alyx-adobe-v-1848961682?fbclid=IwAR1bbUK4gLxKQnlQaHjNcI8rnR3xY4p4iIcBA9lKuDp9QxR_4Sb3IGsVRrw&amp;rev=1653269024116&amp;utm_campaign=Kotaku&amp;utm_content=1653269273&amp;utm_medium=SocialMarketing&amp;utm_source=facebook\">Kotaku</a> and <a href=\"https://80.lv/articles/developer-recreated-their-living-room-in-half-life-alyx/\">80.lv</a> articles :D</div>",
