            "summary": "Made using Maya, Substance Painter, Photoshop, and Unreal Engine.",
            "content_html": "<p class=\"align-center\">Made using Maya, Substance Painter, Photoshop, and Unreal Engine.</p>\n<p class=\"align-center\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/12/workspacevr3smallnew.jpg\" width=\"700\" height=\"933\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/12/responsive/workspacevr3smallnew-xs.jpg 640w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/12/responsive/workspacevr3smallnew-sm.jpg 768w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/12/responsive/workspacevr3smallnew-md.jpg 1024w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/12/responsive/workspacevr3smallnew-lg.jpg 1366w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/12/responsive/workspacevr3smallnew-xl.jpg 1600w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/12/responsive/workspacevr3smallnew-2xl.jpg 1920w\"></p>\n<p> </p>\n<div class=\"align-center\"><a href=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/12/comp1twosmall.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/12/comp1twosmall.jpg\" width=\"700\" height=\"934\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/12/responsive/comp1twosmall-xs.jpg 640w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/12/responsive/comp1twosmall-sm.jpg 768w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/12/responsive/comp1twosmall-md.jpg 1024w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/12/responsive/comp1twosmall-lg.jpg 1366w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/12/responsive/comp1twosmall-xl.jpg 1600w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/12/responsive/comp1twosmall-2xl.jpg 1920w\"></a></div>\n<div> </div>\n<p class=\"align-center\"><a href=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/12/comp2small.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/12/comp2small.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"1140\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/12/responsive/comp2small-xs.jpg 640w ,https://