            "summary": "I remade my living room then blew a hole in the wall. Textures are made using Substance Painter.",
            "content_html": "<p class=\"align-center\">I remade my living room then blew a hole in the wall. Textures are made using Substance Painter.</p>\n<div class=\"align-center\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/13/image-asset2.jpeg\" width=\"700\" height=\"534\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/13/responsive/image-asset2-xs.jpeg 640w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/13/responsive/image-asset2-sm.jpeg 768w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/13/responsive/image-asset2-md.jpeg 1024w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/13/responsive/image-asset2-lg.jpeg 1366w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/13/responsive/image-asset2-xl.jpeg 1600w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/13/responsive/image-asset2-2xl.jpeg 1920w\"></div>\n<div> </div>\n<div class=\"align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiWvRZFlqmP4qnmcmJw0KHs2wDxO9VFJ6-hs0YrNsMehQf02oaMJddY5DpU6olPfha1DXjVv8bU6qONVW2rMX1Q9pZeIi53gEZXiRew0-sfNZEAOgxzCM4AlyEfmcDqnwYhUoeqpqtvVKGyUtolYp2ncZ9cen09H-LnWqoxgr6ZpYjQQuxmViiAe3SLef-T/s1181/image-asset2.jpeg\"> </a></div>\n<div class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"align-center\"><a href=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/13/image-asset4.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/13/image-asset4.jpeg\" width=\"700\" height=\"534\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/13/responsive/image-asset4-xs.jpeg 640w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/13/responsive/image-asset4-sm.jpeg 768w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/13/responsive/image-asset4-md.jpeg 1024w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/13/responsive/image-asset4-lg.jpeg 1366w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/13/responsive/image-asset4-xl.jpeg 1600w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/13/responsive/image-asset4-2xl.jpeg 1920w\"></a></div>\n<div> </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"align-center\"><a href=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/13/image-asset1.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/13/image-asset1.jpeg\" width=\"700\" height=\"534\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/13/responsive/image-asset1-xs.jpeg 640w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/13/responsive/image-asset1-sm.jpeg 768w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/13/responsive/image-asset1-md.jpeg 1024w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/13/responsive/image-asset1-lg.jpeg 1366w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/13/responsive/image-asset1-xl.jpeg 1600w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/13/responsive/image-asset1-2xl.jpeg 1920w\"></a></div>\n</div>",
