        {
            "id": "https://www.grahamrust.me/blog/my-first-3d-print/index.html",
            "url": "https://www.grahamrust.me/blog/my-first-3d-print/index.html",
            "title": "My First 3D Print",
            "summary": "Here's my 3D-printed Oculus Rift made for the Reddit vinyl figure. I simplified a model from VRcover.com and made the facial interface fit the toy. The rest is made from string and ribbon. Original Print. Only cost $6 on Shapeways Also bought a 3D-printed tree&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<p>Here's my 3D-printed Oculus Rift made for the Reddit vinyl figure. I simplified a model from VRcover.com and made the facial interface fit the toy. The rest is made from string and ribbon.</p>\n<div class=\"align-center\"><a href=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/image-asset1.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/image-asset1.jpeg\" width=\"700\" height=\"523\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/responsive/image-asset1-xs.jpeg 640w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/responsive/image-asset1-sm.jpeg 768w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/responsive/image-asset1-md.jpeg 1024w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/responsive/image-asset1-lg.jpeg 1366w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/responsive/image-asset1-xl.jpeg 1600w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/responsive/image-asset1-2xl.jpeg 1920w\"></a></div>\n<div> </div>\n<div> </div>\n<div class=\"align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjewIbzgm7VQyKszzsf5fTQzZfMdahzyp66Th54QradJadhprAusAyXRXAJ6J74l-sYd4uBDg_OenLormYt3tArdf4xtObVCSMLolng79YCul1Zud-82ORlgbqz8k7sHtl3-QhqaSLArNLwJ-28BLRzN4_snVjhOQgbRECYa3iuScreNy7cuUiFEvfGWwj6/s1000/image-asset2.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/image-asset2.jpeg\" width=\"700\" height=\"938\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/responsive/image-asset2-xs.jpeg 640w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/responsive/image-asset2-sm.jpeg 768w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/responsive/image-asset2-md.jpeg 1024w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/responsive/image-asset2-lg.jpeg 1366w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/responsive/image-asset2-xl.jpeg 1600w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/responsive/image-asset2-2xl.jpeg 1920w\"></a></div>\n<div> </div>\n<div> </div>\n<div class=\"align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgtQuJeWpTRwxwgb4n_srDY0qClp_jQ7EQWWkyRAmEtX2_0NAS_w1ZlkIuAWEhWzwRn0Gbe3iqV02P6B4JPJt8oVBKpN5ZFCDIfP4pB38F-RxqdBmYDbjEAXH6FEqpecMBBsjWlUCdDRvYZTdvRPJv_Q4u-emESH3CEXck0cyWpLJij1JCNLOmC-qd_AMbV/s1500/image-asset3.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/image-asset3.jpeg\" width=\"700\" height=\"441\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/responsive/image-asset3-xs.jpeg 640w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/responsive/image-asset3-sm.jpeg 768w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/responsive/image-asset3-md.jpeg 1024w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/responsive/image-asset3-lg.jpeg 1366w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/responsive/image-asset3-xl.jpeg 1600w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/responsive/image-asset3-2xl.jpeg 1920w\"> </a></div>\n<div class=\"align-center\">\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"align-center\"><a href=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/image-asset4.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/image-asset4.png\" alt=\"\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/responsive/image-asset4-xs.png 640w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/responsive/image-asset4-sm.png 768w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/responsive/image-asset4-md.png 1024w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/responsive/image-asset4-lg.png 1366w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/responsive/image-asset4-xl.png 1600w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/responsive/image-asset4-2xl.png 1920w\"></a></p>\n</div>\n<div> </div>\n<div> </div>\n<div class=\"align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhTyJiPDkhZy7aznoNq4hiOLJInF4MYwcf3lphaU8SCMaR_Espjo8yA3bCMIifWjmrFpjWwepWfJha2wu3C-VNh9mITm6g0jfEEew22SmH4dvLBTycmCm5fBbo7INDWyD2qJfOrOocd--hl-5-HR1WMbywrTelNYMN_Qn8imTYMIVAEy9pd-nCKu0izcT28/s1338/image-asset5.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/image-asset5.jpeg\" width=\"700\" height=\"523\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/responsive/image-asset5-xs.jpeg 640w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/responsive/image-asset5-sm.jpeg 768w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/responsive/image-asset5-md.jpeg 1024w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/responsive/image-asset5-lg.jpeg 1366w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/responsive/image-asset5-xl.jpeg 1600w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/responsive/image-asset5-2xl.jpeg 1920w\"></a></div>\n<div> </div>\n<div> </div>\n<div class=\"align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgnymLZHl3Xw2BqTIlbjpkFtJKolq_vsbkeCNTSQkdxIRSSfeGanEmrALuZBX8vmA2T4FY51I_ibmTSxvV0aBBz1VKQLvqk58FKRS2sdjRqIcJA4WIgd6Ceh4HklxyFSWBdaisUPxe79tdAHdzjARvmN4LPuu6Qnunp9UEl36_q5ChvRlQK5_JOtO8pNDvz/s1339/image-asset6.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/image-asset6.jpeg\" width=\"700\" height=\"523\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/responsive/image-asset6-xs.jpeg 640w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/responsive/image-asset6-sm.jpeg 768w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/responsive/image-asset6-md.jpeg 1024w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/responsive/image-asset6-lg.jpeg 1366w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/responsive/image-asset6-xl.jpeg 1600w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/responsive/image-asset6-2xl.jpeg 1920w\"></a></div>\n<div class=\"align-center\">\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"align-center\"><a href=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/7insideoutside.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/7insideoutside.jpg\" alt=\"\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/responsive/7insideoutside-xs.jpg 640w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/responsive/7insideoutside-sm.jpg 768w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/responsive/7insideoutside-md.jpg 1024w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/responsive/7insideoutside-lg.jpg 1366w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/responsive/7insideoutside-xl.jpg 1600w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/responsive/7insideoutside-2xl.jpg 1920w\"></a></p>\n<p class=\"align-center\">Original Print. Only cost $6 on <a href=\"https://www.shapeways.com/product/DRAL824WK/dksnoo?optionId=57528086\" tabindex=\"0\">Shapeways</a></p>\n</div>\n<p class=\"align-center\"><a href=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/image-asset8.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/image-asset8.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"523\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/responsive/image-asset8-xs.jpeg 640w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/responsive/image-asset8-sm.jpeg 768w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/responsive/image-asset8-md.jpeg 1024w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/responsive/image-asset8-lg.jpeg 1366w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/responsive/image-asset8-xl.jpeg 1600w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/responsive/image-asset8-2xl.jpeg 1920w\"></a></p>\n<p class=\"align-center\">Also bought a 3D-printed tree based on Darwin's drawing</p>\n<div class=\"align-center\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhAiUZIT4KvPsK6D5-fhVrheXZXcfnVkXiieuNhed4vv4QzVjtVk18Ooix0cwFmz8c-4baUspkZlDiqBy1kl_ZOmwR8Osry2ll8wzNEinZjyPRbbw3nEE8VQwBmmfSW17Sk0_feg4GBgrGdojCZ_YFqxh2KV-QqqksGALP7UKEUumCFF9mix-9S7yKg3ANm/s1339/image-asset8.jpeg\"> </a></div>\n<p class=\"align-center\"><a href=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/image-asset9.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/image-asset9.jpeg\" alt=\"\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/responsive/image-asset9-xs.jpeg 640w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/responsive/image-asset9-sm.jpeg 768w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/responsive/image-asset9-md.jpeg 1024w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/responsive/image-asset9-lg.jpeg 1366w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/responsive/image-asset9-xl.jpeg 1600w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/14/responsive/image-asset9-2xl.jpeg 1920w\"></a></p>\n<p class=\"align-center\">Cat for scale :D Thanks for checking out my print! Back to <a href=\"https://www.reddit.com/r/oculus/comments/3ipteb/a_15_scale_3dprinted_dk2_made_it_for_my_snoo_but/\" tabindex=\"0\">Reddit</a></p>",
