            "id": "https://www.grahamrust.me/blog/workspace-comparisons-4/index.html",
            "url": "https://www.grahamrust.me/blog/workspace-comparisons-4/index.html",
            "title": "Workspace Comparisons",
            "summary": "Here are some comparison pictures of my actual/VR workspace: The current look is inspired by Berlin Flat on the UE4 marketplace My workspace is in my closet I eliminated cables and other unnecessary things that I won't be touching in the virtual environment So many&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<p>Here are some comparison pictures of my actual/VR workspace:</p>\n<p class=\"align-center\"><a href=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/image-asset.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/image-asset.jpeg\" alt=\"\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/responsive/image-asset-xs.jpeg 640w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/responsive/image-asset-sm.jpeg 768w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/responsive/image-asset-md.jpeg 1024w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/responsive/image-asset-lg.jpeg 1366w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/responsive/image-asset-xl.jpeg 1600w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/responsive/image-asset-2xl.jpeg 1920w\"></a></p>\n<p class=\"align-center\">The current look is inspired by Berlin Flat on the UE4 marketplace</p>\n<p class=\"align-center\"><a href=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/image-asset2.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/image-asset2.jpeg\" alt=\"\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/responsive/image-asset2-xs.jpeg 640w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/responsive/image-asset2-sm.jpeg 768w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/responsive/image-asset2-md.jpeg 1024w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/responsive/image-asset2-lg.jpeg 1366w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/responsive/image-asset2-xl.jpeg 1600w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/responsive/image-asset2-2xl.jpeg 1920w\"></a></p>\n<p class=\"align-center\">My workspace is in my closet</p>\n<div class=\"align-center\">\n<p class=\"align-center\"><a href=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/image-asset3.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/image-asset3.jpeg\" alt=\"\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/responsive/image-asset3-xs.jpeg 640w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/responsive/image-asset3-sm.jpeg 768w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/responsive/image-asset3-md.jpeg 1024w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/responsive/image-asset3-lg.jpeg 1366w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/responsive/image-asset3-xl.jpeg 1600w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/responsive/image-asset3-2xl.jpeg 1920w\"></a></p>\n<p class=\"align-center\">I eliminated cables and other unnecessary things that I won't be touching in the virtual environment</p>\n</div>\n<p class=\"align-center\"><a href=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/image-asset4.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/image-asset4.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"699\" height=\"261\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/responsive/image-asset4-xs.jpeg 640w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/responsive/image-asset4-sm.jpeg 768w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/responsive/image-asset4-md.jpeg 1024w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/responsive/image-asset4-lg.jpeg 1366w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/responsive/image-asset4-xl.jpeg 1600w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/responsive/image-asset4-2xl.jpeg 1920w\"></a></p>\n<p class=\"align-center\">So many input devices; Touchscreen monitor, Wacom tablet, trackball mouse, racing wheel, controllers</p>\n<div class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"align-center\"><br>\n<p class=\"align-center\"><a href=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/image-asset5.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/image-asset5.jpeg\" alt=\"\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/responsive/image-asset5-xs.jpeg 640w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/responsive/image-asset5-sm.jpeg 768w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/responsive/image-asset5-md.jpeg 1024w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/responsive/image-asset5-lg.jpeg 1366w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/responsive/image-asset5-xl.jpeg 1600w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/responsive/image-asset5-2xl.jpeg 1920w\"></a></p>\n<p class=\"align-center\">Slimmed down G27 racing setup. Used a picture of Palmer Luckey and the Portal colors to change things up</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"align-center\">\n<p class=\"align-center\"><a href=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/image-asset7.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/image-asset7.jpeg\" alt=\"\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/responsive/image-asset7-xs.jpeg 640w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/responsive/image-asset7-sm.jpeg 768w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/responsive/image-asset7-md.jpeg 1024w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/responsive/image-asset7-lg.jpeg 1366w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/responsive/image-asset7-xl.jpeg 1600w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/responsive/image-asset7-2xl.jpeg 1920w\"></a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"align-center\">\n<p class=\"align-center\"><a href=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/image-asset6.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/image-asset6.jpeg\" alt=\"\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/responsive/image-asset6-xs.jpeg 640w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/responsive/image-asset6-sm.jpeg 768w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/responsive/image-asset6-md.jpeg 1024w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/responsive/image-asset6-lg.jpeg 1366w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/responsive/image-asset6-xl.jpeg 1600w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/responsive/image-asset6-2xl.jpeg 1920w\"></a></p>\n<p class=\"align-center\">My current project is a life drawing studio. I use the trackball mouse to rotate the model and sun, and my Wacom tablet to draw. I play music using 3D audio coming from the speakers</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"align-center\">\n<p class=\"align-center\"><a href=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/image-asset8.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/image-asset8.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"701\" height=\"262\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/responsive/image-asset8-xs.jpeg 640w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/responsive/image-asset8-sm.jpeg 768w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/responsive/image-asset8-md.jpeg 1024w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/responsive/image-asset8-lg.jpeg 1366w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/responsive/image-asset8-xl.jpeg 1600w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/responsive/image-asset8-2xl.jpeg 1920w\"></a></p>\n<p class=\"align-center\">Character models are taken from a 3DS game</p>\n<div class=\"align-center\"> </div>\n</div>\n<p class=\"align-center\"><a href=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/image-asset10.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/image-asset10.jpeg\" alt=\"\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/responsive/image-asset10-xs.jpeg 640w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/responsive/image-asset10-sm.jpeg 768w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/responsive/image-asset10-md.jpeg 1024w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/responsive/image-asset10-lg.jpeg 1366w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/responsive/image-asset10-xl.jpeg 1600w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/responsive/image-asset10-2xl.jpeg 1920w\"></a></p>\n<p class=\"align-center\">Thankfully Tomodachi Life for 3DS had a high poly cat that looked just like mine :P</p>\n<p class=\"align-center\"><a href=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/image-asset11.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/image-asset11.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"699\" height=\"261\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/responsive/image-asset11-xs.jpeg 640w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/responsive/image-asset11-sm.jpeg 768w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/responsive/image-asset11-md.jpeg 1024w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/responsive/image-asset11-lg.jpeg 1366w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/responsive/image-asset11-xl.jpeg 1600w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/responsive/image-asset11-2xl.jpeg 1920w\"></a></p>\n<p class=\"align-center\">much poly so realism</p>\n<p>Join the discussion on <a href=\"http://www.reddit.com/r/oculus/comments/35tl60/wip_recreating_my_bedroomworkspace_in_ue4_here/\" tabindex=\"0\">Reddit</a></p>",
            "image": "https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/15/image-asset.jpg",
            "author": {
                "name": "Graham Rust"
            },
            "tags": [
            ],
            "date_published": "2015-05-13T16:00:00-04:00",
            "date_modified": "2026-06-04T23:22:57-04:00"
