        {
            "id": "https://www.grahamrust.me/blog/recreating-workspace-for-vr/index.html",
            "url": "https://www.grahamrust.me/blog/recreating-workspace-for-vr/index.html",
            "title": "Recreating workspace for VR",
            "summary": "My current project is a 1:1 copy of my bedroom and computer room. I would like to build little VR experiments within my room. I could also augment items in my room, such as removing the roof to see the stars at night.",
            "content_html": "<p>My current project is a 1:1 copy of my bedroom and computer room. I would like to build little VR experiments within my room. I could also augment items in my room, such as removing the roof to see the stars at night.</p>\n<p class=\"align-center\"><a href=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/16/roomue4.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/16/roomue4.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"368\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/16/responsive/roomue4-xs.jpeg 640w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/16/responsive/roomue4-sm.jpeg 768w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/16/responsive/roomue4-md.jpeg 1024w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/16/responsive/roomue4-lg.jpeg 1366w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/16/responsive/roomue4-xl.jpeg 1600w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/16/responsive/roomue4-2xl.jpeg 1920w\"></a></p>\n<p class=\"align-center\"><a href=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/16/ScreenShot00003.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/16/ScreenShot00003.jpg\" alt=\"\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/16/responsive/ScreenShot00003-xs.jpg 640w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/16/responsive/ScreenShot00003-sm.jpg 768w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/16/responsive/ScreenShot00003-md.jpg 1024w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/16/responsive/ScreenShot00003-lg.jpg 1366w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/16/responsive/ScreenShot00003-xl.jpg 1600w ,https://www.grahamrust.me/media/posts/16/responsive/ScreenShot00003-2xl.jpg 1920w\"></a></p>",
